  "texts": [
    "When asked about the installation of wind turbines in desert areas it warns about the potential impact of dust on blades (Box 2).",
    "It can even give you hints on what could be the best commercial activity for a particular place, considering future climate change (Box 3).",
    "Using ClimSight to obtain guidance on future projects is costeffective: a query to ClimSight costs approximately 6 cents per query using OpenAI GPT-4 API, once the underlying data and climate model simulations are in place.",
    "From proof-of-concept to global service In our view, there are two particularly encouraging avenues for the enhancement of our proof-of-concept prototype ClimSight that merit further elaboration.",
    "First, it looks promising to expand the information available for the specified location, for example using high-resolution geographical data and highly detailed climate information."
